Split Data

set.seed(689)
test = sample(1:256004,50000,F)
flight.test = flight.w[test,]
flight.train = flight.w[-test,]

Model Fitting

Model W0-1 : fit only weather variables

logis.w01 = glm(DelayOver60~Temp.+DewPoint+Humidity+Pressure+Visibility+Wind.Dir+
                  Wind.Speed+Gust.Speed+Conditions,
             family = binomial(link = "logit"),data=flight.train)

x.col = names(logis.w01$model) %>% .[-1]
pred.p = predict(logis.w01, newdata=flight.test[,x.col], type="response")
threshold = flight.w$DelayOver60 %>% as.character() %>% as.numeric() %>% mean()
pred.01 = ifelse(pred.p>threshold,1,0)
true.p = flight.test$DelayOver60
(confu.tb = table(pred.01,true.p))
##        true.p
## pred.01     0     1
##       0 34835  1748
##       1 11409  2008
sprintf("accuracy: %f",(confu.tb[1,1]+confu.tb[2,2])/dim(flight.test)[1])
## [1] "accuracy: 0.736860"
sprintf("recall: %f",confu.tb[2,2]/sum(confu.tb[,2]) )
## [1] "recall: 0.534611"
sprintf("precision: %f",confu.tb[2,2]/sum(confu.tb[2,]))
## [1] "precision: 0.149661"
#
pr = prediction(pred.p, true.p)
prf = performance(pr, measure = "tpr", x.measure = "fpr")
auc = performance(pr, measure = "auc")
(auc = auc@y.values[[1]])
## [1] 0.6961523
plot(prf)
abline(a=0,b=1,col="red",lty=2)

summary(logis.w01)

Model W0-9 : add Wind.Speed/Wind.Dir/Dest interaction term:

logis.w09 = glm(DelayOver60~Temp.+Humidity+Pressure+Visibility+Wind.Dir+
                  Wind.Speed+Gust.Speed+Conditions+Dest+
                  Dest*Wind.Dir+Dest*Wind.Speed+Wind.Speed*Wind.Dir+Dest*Wind.Dir*Wind.Speed,
                family = binomial(link = "logit"),data=flight.train)

x.col = names(logis.w09$model) %>% .[-1]
pred.p = predict(logis.w09, newdata=flight.test[,x.col], type="response")
## Warning in predict.lm(object, newdata, se.fit, scale = 1, type =
